document_data.Notable Owners:
*[[Clas Denwith]], a General from [[Arrabar]] and a [[priest]] of [[Tempus]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.
*[[Guthbert Golthammer]], a [[Zhent]]-appointed constable of [[Dagger Falls]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.
*[[Llachior Blackthorn]], the Duke of the Duchy of [[Cape Velen]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.{{Cite dragon/182/Kings of the Caravans|48}}
*[[Kalima]], or "Bounce", a [[half-elven]] [[bard]] who showed no evidence of her [[fey]] blood, active in [[Ravens Bluff]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.{{Cite polyhedron/79/The Living City: The Painted Boat Restaurant|18}}
